This is version 0.0.2

you should be able to build and install gevas simply by running 

./autogen.sh
make

and then you can test by running the demo :
demo/testgevas

The following are some interesting things...


To use gevas inside a gtk_scrolled_window one must add it 
using gtk_scrolled_window_add_with_viewport()


I have tried to model some of the API after GnomeCanvas.

